In the first round of combat, all critical hits scored by the Rogue Trader's party inflict burning. In addition, all fire damage suffered by enemies is increased by +1 for each Conviction: Imperialis rank.{br}
<align="center"> ///Imperialis — Adherent -//
<i>Burning:</i> at the start of every turn the affected target suffers 10 damage and must pass an Agility resistance test with a −10 penalty to stop burning.

